### Custom Labels, Custom Settings & Custom Metadata

```
# Custom Labels - UPPER_SNAKE_CASE or PascalCase
ERROR_INVALID_ACCOUNT
SUCCESS_RECORD_SAVED
ValidationError_RequiredField

# Custom Settings - PascalCase + "Settings" suffix
AccountSettings__c
IntegrationSettings__c
FeatureFlags__c

# Custom Metadata Types - PascalCase + "Config" or "Mapping" suffix
CountryCodeMapping__mdt
FieldValidationConfig__mdt
IntegrationEndpoint__mdt

# Custom Permissions - PascalCase, descriptive
CanEditClosedOpportunity
CanViewSensitiveData
