| Controller | PascalCase + `Controller` | `AccountController` |
| Test Class | ClassName + `Test` | `AccountServiceTest` |
| Trigger | ObjectName + `Trigger` | `AccountTrigger` |
| VF Page | PascalCase | `AccountDetail` |
| LWC | camelCase | `accountDetail` |
| Aura Component | PascalCase | `AccountDetail` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `MAX_RETRY_COUNT` |
| Variables | camelCase | `accountName` |
| Custom Label | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `ERROR_NOT_FOUND` |
